{"tid":513951,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"內置豎中指 Emoji WhatsApp 印度面臨刑事起訴","createTime":"2017-12-30T05:50:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-30T09:19:42.000Z","uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5e625f4f288ffbbe78abea411b48e49e0e6935fe","tid":513951,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T05:50:25.000Z","msg":"不少人在 WhatsApp 發訊息時加入 Emoji 表情符號，因為簡單的一個符號往往可以代替很多文字，表達我們的心情和感受。不過最近即時通訊軟件 WhatsApp 卻因為一個「豎中指」的 Emoji，可能會在印度面臨民事或刑事起訴。<br />\n<br />\n事緣一名印度律師 Gurmeet Singh 日前警告 WhatsApp，表示假如印度刑法 354 和 509 條，向女士展示猥褻、淫蕩或冒犯的手勢，或任何人使用猥褻、淫蕩或冒犯的手勢都屬違法。WhatsApp 內置「豎中指」Emoji 就是直接教唆使用上述不法的手勢。Singh 要求 WhatsApp 在 15 天內將「豎中指」Emoji 移除，否則就會訴諸法律，考慮透過民事或刑事方式起訴對方。"},{"pid":"03710f30701cbbd97b50ac359c14d157e4226c55","tid":513951,"uid":2076,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T06:29:36.000Z","msg":"理好性侵先理對女性嘅專重啦<br />\n<br />\n#metoo<br />\n#staystrong"},{"pid":"ff0784b395b295180940ee20a9ab211f30f4f0e8","tid":513951,"uid":137291,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T08:04:53.000Z","msg":"印度原來有法例保障女性?<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"079d1f38d0aceb08723cc0a95045c8d1c17e71a3","tid":513951,"uid":127123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T08:14:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  幾時告埋連登?"},{"pid":"f4e022cdd644ab7e66af29dca2ca1df78ac5a8c1","tid":513951,"uid":6366,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T08:17:21.000Z","msg":"睇到印度真係笑出聲<br />\n唔舉得中指 只可以舉丁"},{"pid":"61e9cf86b74a1b5a590dd1ec2cdfcf1a66212257","tid":513951,"uid":96743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T09:04:32.000Z","msg":"印度有法律保護女性<br />\n多謝呢位律師提供2017最好笑既笑話<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"290dcd702d57137d63d2d4c2b25160841becb68d","tid":513951,"uid":4677,"like":0,